title: And Also The Trees Discography
description:
Hi guys, here is the discography of And Also The Trees. I think this is about it...I checked everywhere and couldn't find anything else. I'm sorry the audio isn't that good (sometimes even horrible) but it's really hard to find some good stuff these days. 
Please seed as much as you can !

This includes :

1980 Malvern Demos (tape)
1982 From Under the Hills (tape)
1983 Shantell EP
1984 And Also The Trees
1984 The Secret Sea EP
1985 A Room Lives In Lucy EP
1986 Virus Meadow
1987 The Critical Distance EP
1987 (Live) The Evening Of The 24th
1987 The Millpond Years
1988 (Live) Grenoble
1989 Farewell To The Shade
1992 Green Is The Sea
1993 The Klaxon
1996 Angelfish
1998 Silver Soul
2003 Further From The Truth
2007 (Listen For) The Rag & Bone Man
2009 And Also The Trees EP
2011 Driftwood
2011 Hunter Not The Hunted
2012 (Live) La Laiterie
